dcterms:description: A synthetic dataset generated from dynamic simulations of line trip and generation loss events in the Texas 2000-bus synthetic grid using the power system simulator for engineering (PSS(E)). The dataset includes measurements from PMUs across the grid during various events.
dcterms:title: Texas 2000-bus synthetic grid

dcterms:description: A proprietary dataset with labeled events obtained from a large utility in the USA, involving measurements from nearly 500 PMUs. The dataset includes labeled generation loss and line trip events.
dcterms:title: Proprietary dataset with labeled events
